\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6636965 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14686165\charrsid13851071 Did this apply to the young children?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11944731 HS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14686165\charrsid13851071 Yes, it was right through, yes. Although - 
not in this occasion - not for grandmother. It was only when - mother died that - well, of course we were all - see, Jim would be about twelve or fourteen then I think. But it was - of course, that's been the only death - mother and father were the only d
eaths in the family. But it was mourning all through.
