\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11944731 HS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14686165\charrsid13851071 No, I'm sorry - I - like when - no, when mother died of course - they were scarcely wearing the clothes up.
