\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6636965 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14686165\charrsid13851071 Did he often take you to visit people?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11944731 HS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14686165\charrsid13851071 No, I wouldn't say it was often - just occasionally.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6636965 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14686165\charrsid13851071 You didn't visit neighbours?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11944731 HS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14686165\charrsid13851071 No. No.
