as going. But I don't think we were taken shopping much apart from that.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6636965 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14686165\charrsid13851071 It wasn't part of your weekly routine to go to the market you\rquote re your mother?
