- the whole family used to go - I think it was - I don't know if it was from church or where - we used to get a wagonette - two horse wagonette and go to - Whittle Springs round about }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7437536\charrsid13851071 
Headington}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14686165\charrsid13851071  or Chorley there. Oh, this happened a few times. And of course that was a days outing then.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6636965 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14686165\charrsid13851071 Was this just for the family?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11944731 HS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14686165\charrsid13851071 No. Family and friends. They used to engage this - vehicle. Then on t}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7437536\charrsid13851071 w}{
\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14686165\charrsid13851071 o }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7437536\charrsid13851071 other}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14686165\charrsid13851071 
 occasions there'd be one or two from church and of course all family had joined and gone. But - oh yes, the family had a few of these - efforts.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6636965 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14686165\charrsid13851071 You've mentioned holidays haven't you?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11944731 HS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14686165\charrsid13851071 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6636965 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14686165\charrsid13851071 Did you used to go away regularly?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11944731 HS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14686165\charrsid13851071 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6636965 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14686165\charrsid13851071 Every Summer?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11944731 HS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14686165\charrsid13851071 Every summer.
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6636965 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14686165\charrsid13851071 Would this be far a week?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11944731 HS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14686165\charrsid13851071 Yes. Well - yes, usually about eight days. But we were used to go on a Sunday when it wasn't quite so crowded.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6636965 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14686165\charrsid13851071 Did your father get a full weeks holiday when you were children?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11944731 HS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14686165\charrsid13851071 Yes, yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6636965 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14686165\charrsid13851071 Did all the family go away for the holiday?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11944731 HS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14686165\charrsid13851071 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6636965 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14686165\charrsid13851071 Where would you normally go to?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11944731 HS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14686165\charrsid13851071 Fleetwood. And - I know we used to take apartments.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6636965 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14686165\charrsid13851071 What sort of things did you do while you were on holiday?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11944731 HS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14686165\charrsid13851071 Well invariably we were on the beach all day and every day. The only time they saw us was at meal times.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6636965 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14686165\charrsid13851071 Did your parents leave you completely free?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11944731 HS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14686165\charrsid13851071 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6636965 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14686165\charrsid13851071 To go off?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11944731 HS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14686165\charrsid13851071 Yes. We could amuse ourselves as best we could. But we must appear at meal times. And of course that suited us as well.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6636965 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14686165\charrsid13851071 Have you any idea how they spent their time?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11944731 HS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14686165\charrsid13851071 Haven't the foggiest. But then I never asked.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6636965 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14686165\charrsid13851071 How did you spend your Saturdays as a child?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11944731 HS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14686165\charrsid13851071 
Well invariably there was some little household chores in the morning or errands. And then - played football in the afternoon or cricket. Then the evening - oh, just seemed
 to come indoors - this would be up to what - about twelve or fourteen I should say - then we used to come indoors and read and make our own amusements in the house. Read and play games.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6636965 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14686165\charrsid13851071 And Sundays?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11944731 HS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14686165\charrsid13851071 Always went to church. Yes. Morning, afternoon and evening. Well, Sunday school in the afternoon.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6636965 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14686165\charrsid13851071 Did you have special clothes for Sunday?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11944731 HS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14686165\charrsid13851071 Yes. Oh yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6636965 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14686165\charrsid13851071 Did you play games at all on a Sunday?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11944731 HS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14686165\charrsid13851071 Not officially. We did but - it was only done to - parents. Otherwise we should have been in trouble.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6636965 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14686165\charrsid13851071 Did your parents think it was wrong to work or play on a Sunday?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11944731 HS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14686165\charrsid13851071 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6636965 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14686165\charrsid13851071 How did you manage to play without them knowing - did you play outside?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11944731 HS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14686165\charrsid13851071 Well - outside - oh yes, away from home. Then of course was our job polishing our shoes and whatnot before we went in.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6636965 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14686165\charrsid13851071 Were you wearing your best clothes while you were out?
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11944731 HS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14686165\charrsid13851071 
Oh yes, yes. Oh yes. I - I don't know whether the parents realised it or not but they had the idea that if we were in our best clothes we shouldn't play. But I'm afraid if they did think that their child psychology was sadly at fault.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6636965 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14686165\charrsid13851071 It was Church of England wasn't it?
