Not Sunday mornings. Most Sunday evenings and she managed to get - the mid week service in - Thur - usually Thursday morning. She was her communion then.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6636965 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14686165\charrsid13851071 Were there any Sunday school outings that you can remember?
