\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6636965 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14686165\charrsid13851071 Did the church run any temperance club - Band of Hope or anything like that?
