\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6636965 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14686165\charrsid13851071 And you belonged to this?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11944731 HS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14686165\charrsid13851071 Yes, oh yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6636965 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14686165\charrsid13851071 Did you belong to any other club that the church organised?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11944731 HS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14686165\charrsid13851071 No, I don't know that I did. In fact I don't think there was anything then. They didn't have any scouts or Boys Brigade or -
